title.rendered: DRIVETECH 4X4 High Lift Jack – Wheel Lift

content.rendered: For use with Drivetech 4×4 high lift jack this special tool has two rubber coated steel hooks that allow your 48″ High lift jack to safely lift from the wheels of most 4×4 vehicles.
